---
title: Double Mumbai-Spiced Prawn & Veggie Curry with Garlic Rice & Peanuts
description: If you’re looking for a cosy meal to add to the table, we can’t recommend this rich prawn and veggie curry enough. Let the
warmth of Mumbai spice and coconut add extra layers of flavour, and serve over garlic rice for another boost. You’ll be humming in bliss with every bite!
